</node>
<node id="Annual Report on Form 10-K">
  <data key="d0">Annual Report on Form 10-K</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a document that includes NVIDIA's Consolidated Financial Statements, related Notes, and other cautionary statements and risks, which is used to provide a comprehensive view of the company's financial condition and operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a comprehensive report filed annually by companies to disclose financial performance and other significant information to investors and regulators.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a comprehensive report that includes KLAC's financial statements, management's discussion and analysis, and other important information about the company's financial condition, results of operations, and more.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is an annual report that provides a comprehensive overview of a company's financial performance and is filed with the SEC.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f0b30e55c2d2c942c8ef27807467b3d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91ba0c40d4695fe5428e9f1aaee99693&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4612ab0f41075ef25aa4070b5715ec41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19032b9d0addd28842932a48ea8fd697</data>
