<node id="Research and Development">
  <data key="d0">Research and Development</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Research and development expenses for fiscal year 2026 were $18,497 million, showing a 43% increase from the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and development is a critical activity for the company's future success, with significant resources allocated to developing new products.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and development is a core business function critical for future success, involving significant investment in new products and technology development.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and Development is a category of expenses that increased by 5% for the company in the fiscal year ended March 31, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;It refers to the company's policies and activities related to research and development.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and Development refers to the company's investments in creating new products and technologies, critical for securing design wins and maintaining market share.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and Development is a category within the financial report, showing expenses and percentages for different fiscal years.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-db98b1c09ec551c8a83f9131498334c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5068f4b1da4cd023617e872a463eeb62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b11abf58ed4d75a128d8d943d08096f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a917696681899c306badc63ac69b7d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca207bb382651453029b45cb72e9feff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da2b01ab4070bbe76a7dd3d4ffb383d7</data>
