<node id="Form 10-K">
  <data key="d0">Form 10-K</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Form 10-K is an annual report that includes a summary of significant accounting policies and financial statements.&lt;SEP&gt;Form 10-K is the content of the Annual Report which contains Notes to the Consolidated Financial Statements.&lt;SEP&gt;Form 10-K is an annual report filed with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission that discloses a company's financial performance and outstanding shares for a fiscal year.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Form 10-K is a financial report filed by AMD with the Securities and Exchange Commission.&lt;SEP&gt;Form 10-K is an annual report filed by companies with the Securities and Exchange Commission.&lt;SEP&gt;Form 10-K is an annual report filed by the company with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, detailing its financial performance and other significant information.&lt;SEP&gt;Form 10-K is the annual report form filed with the SEC that includes the company's Consolidated Financial Statements and details on goodwill impairment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fe1fafd9b0c6f09af84ad373757a9b00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a36df99dfa3a16bd8e4d429df7cf42a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737963f5a4aa4c7ac5ff75bd66cabe60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1329332311e82d0b2cc6f7232bfaa092&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d780eacfb91e291d22055bf3aca31fa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3082390d4ae9b34c69f94e2ec0135c5</data>
