  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The H20 excess inventory and purchase obligations resulted in a $4.5 billion charge for NVIDIA in the first quarter of fiscal year 2026, affecting the company's operating income.&lt;SEP&gt;H20 excess inventory refers to the overstock of H20 products that led to a $4.5 billion charge, impacting the gross margin.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fe1fafd9b0c6f09af84ad373757a9b00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd5f5a1a7c540b1c8cafe05b35cfd7fb</data>
