<node id="Board of Directors">
  <data key="d0">Board of Directors</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Board of Directors is a group of individuals elected by shareholders to oversee the management of the company and make key decisions. This governing body is responsible for making decisions regarding the payment of dividends and share repurchases, always considering the best interest of stockholders. In addition to financial matters, the Board of Directors is also tasked with overseeing the company's major risks, including cybersecurity risks. They are responsible for considering the grant date fair value for share-based awards in the context of ordinary share valuations. The Board of Directors has the authority to approve important company actions, such as the authorization to repurchase shares. In the case of INTC, the Board of Directors has authorized the repurchase of common stock, demonstrating their role in significant corporate decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Directors is the governing body that approves and amends authorizations for the company's activities, including share repurchases.|&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Directors of KLA Corporation declared a quarterly cash dividend on the company's common stock.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Directors is a governing body responsible for making decisions regarding the declaration and payment of cash dividends.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Directors is a group of individuals who are elected to represent the interests of all shareholders and oversee the company's management.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a36df99dfa3a16bd8e4d429df7cf42a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b976a275590777e7877d2d66b5f6379c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-625ca1cf50e3b24380c8601c96bdd7a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f533007cd8f65f3f88984fedd522d05d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1fc03c6340e9f91435287101b7ba57e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f60be1d369008dda0461cefaf2ff61fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4845686f7704c5c80e402305d19f7ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77d86694dce1fc1e9c3d3ac3bab4c5be&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01ee832930ff813d9db8fa5bfa02507e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0875cdce54018cd923f6cab7e6b6692&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a23fd7a348fc3f448641e9ef7d5be33a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d780eacfb91e291d22055bf3aca31fa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-541097656a29c150756d08c4943ad8b0</data>
