  <data key="d0">Fiscal Year 2025</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Fiscal Year 2025 is the previous fiscal year for which NVIDIA reported financial data, used as a comparative period for analyzing changes in revenue and expenses.&lt;SEP&gt;Fiscal Year 2025 is a period during which the company spent $3.4 billion on capital expenditures.&lt;SEP&gt;Fiscal Year 2025 is the time period in which the company experienced an increase in revenue and improved financial performance despite challenges from tariffs.&lt;SEP&gt;The fiscal year 2025 is a period that ended on June 30, 2025, during which R&amp;D expenses and other financial activities were recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;The Fiscal Year 2025 is a specific period that ended on June 30, 2025, during which the company experienced a 24% increase in total revenues.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd5f5a1a7c540b1c8cafe05b35cfd7fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91ba0c40d4695fe5428e9f1aaee99693&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4cef59817c38511355f56938f73f6db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0f7533f1c0231555ac5ae30f4d37842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8c3943d4fcccf1ae19651cf71f87bf4</data>
