  <data key="d1">financialliability</data>
  <data key="d2">Unrecognized Tax Benefits of $4.0 billion include related interest and penalties of $374 million, recorded in non-current income tax payable at the end of fiscal year 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;The Unrecognized Tax Benefits with a gross liability of $452 million as of October 26, 2025, are not expected to result in payment of cash within one year.&lt;SEP&gt;Unrecognized Tax Benefits are reserves included in the provision for income taxes, along with related net interest and penalties.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Unrecognized tax benefits are potential tax positions that have not been recorded on a company's financial statements due to uncertainty.</data>
