  <data key="d2">Capital equipment refers to the equipment at customer sites used for patterning, transistor, interconnect, process control, and packaging performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Capital Equipment refers to the machinery and equipment used by businesses in their operations, significant in industries like semiconductor manufacturing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e7481c513c84b894dbf5566a03c9c31d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b07cc11b6e49549f800863a0e198d15c</data>
