<node id="AGS Segment">
  <data key="d0">AGS Segment</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The AGS segment is a part of a company that provides services, spares, and factory automation software globally to customer fabrication plants, optimizing the performance of semiconductor and other equipment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e7481c513c84b894dbf5566a03c9c31d</data>
