  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Foundry is a type of customer for Semiconductor Systems, accounting for a percentage of net revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;Foundry is a segment within the Semiconductor Systems division of Applied Materials, Inc., accounting for a percentage of the total revenue.</data>
