<node id="200mm Equipment">
  <data key="d0">200mm Equipment</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The 200mm equipment refers to machinery used in semiconductor manufacturing, with a wafer diameter of 200mm.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The 200mm equipment refers to a specific type of equipment used in semiconductor manufacturing that is part of the AGS segment's offerings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e7481c513c84b894dbf5566a03c9c31d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f50e3434e5c216500628bf58a9da4be1</data>
