<node id="Applied Global Services">
  <data key="d0">Applied Global Services</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Applied Global Services is a business segment that reported an operating income of $1,792 million in 2025, showing a 1% decrease from 2024.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Global Services is the full name of the AGS segment, providing services, spares, and factory automation software globally.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Global Services is a segment of the company that derives a majority of its revenue from sales to semiconductor manufacturers.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Global Services is a division of Applied Materials, Inc. that delivered record services and spares revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Global Services is a segment of Applied Materials, Inc. with its own revenue, gross margin, and operating income figures.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Global Services is a category within Applied Materials, Inc.'s financial report, detailing the performance of their global services business segment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e7481c513c84b894dbf5566a03c9c31d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-528b15deb865d055e3be525ecf5963bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf53d552d1955a280cebbd6e2d050c2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-531a2d4da0efcbaa075b41456e2d3536&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1e351045874ef4f72c98449caf3e612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2955967583e4d17eefb4b391be0c469</data>
