<node id="Global Trade Issues">
  <data key="d0">Global Trade Issues</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Global trade issues encompass a range of factors such as trade policies, export regulations, tariffs, and international trade disputes that affect the company's business and operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Global trade issues encompass changes and uncertainties related to trade regulations, policies, sanctions, tariffs, and international disputes, particularly those involving technology exports to China.&lt;SEP&gt;Global trade issues include changes in trade and export regulations, trade policies, and sanctions that impact Our Business.&lt;SEP&gt;Global Trade Issues include changes and uncertainties in trade policies, import and export licenses, trade sanctions, tariffs, and international trade disputes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e7481c513c84b894dbf5566a03c9c31d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf53d552d1955a280cebbd6e2d050c2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b0f36135b3b08cac0302bf342d7918d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-120a4f2fbe48d0891e48fba271c88ec1</data>
