<node id="Advanced Packaging">
  <data key="d0">Advanced Packaging</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Advanced packaging refers to sophisticated methods used in the assembly and packaging of semiconductor devices.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced packaging is a technique that is increasingly important for AI computing.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced Packaging refers to the latest techniques in packaging semiconductor devices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f50e3434e5c216500628bf58a9da4be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5492aef4a6baa648ca24a791f135e6fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3082390d4ae9b34c69f94e2ec0135c5</data>
