<node id="Electric and Autonomous Vehicles">
  <data key="d0">Electric and Autonomous Vehicles</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Electric and autonomous vehicles refer to vehicles that are powered by electricity and have the ability to drive without human input.&gt;</data>
