  <data key="d0">Singapore</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Singapore is a country where the company has been granted additional conditional reduced tax rates expiring beginning in fiscal 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a country where the company has been granted additional conditional reduced tax rates, which are set to expire beginning in fiscal 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a location where the organization has been granted conditional reduced tax rates, which are set to expire beginning in fiscal 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a location where Applied Materials, Inc. has operations affected by new tax incentive agreements, impacting the company's income tax provisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a location where the company has significant manufacturing operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is one of the foreign jurisdictions where the company earns a majority of its non-U.S. profits and is potentially subject to taxes.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a foreign jurisdiction where the company earns a majority of its non-U.S. profits and is subject to tax rates that may change.</data>
