  <data key="d1">financialobligation</data>
  <data key="d2">The Operating Lease Obligation is $565 million related to various operating lease arrangements for certain facilities as of October 26, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;The Operating Lease Obligation is a financial obligation of the entity related to operating leases.</data>
