<node id="October 26, 2025">
  <data key="d0">October 26, 2025</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">October 26, 2025 is the date when the company had approximately $14.0 billion remaining available for future stock repurchases under the repurchase program.&lt;SEP&gt;October 26, 2025 is the date as of which the company's financial data, such as notes, lease obligations, and other obligations, are reported.&lt;SEP&gt;October 26, 2025 is the date as of which the organization had $6.5 billion in aggregate principal amount of senior unsecured notes outstanding.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3f659a7f219f7f617d5e8dc482fab75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b976a275590777e7877d2d66b5f6379c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7200d8553fd2e4a1586cd2f8af4129fc</data>
