  <data key="d2">AMAT is a company that provides equipment, services, and software to the semiconductor and related industries. It is involved in Management’s Discussion and Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations (MD&amp;A) and has strategic priorities in product development and market expansion.&gt;</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0</data>
