<node id="Managements Discussion and Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations">
  <data key="d0">Managements Discussion and Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Management’s Discussion and Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations (MD&amp;A) is a section of the document that aims to provide an understanding of the company's business and financial results. It is to be read with the Consolidated Financial Statements and other parts of the Form 10-K.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;It is a section in the Annual Report on Form 20-F that discusses the company's financial health and operational results, including liquidity and capital resources.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a917696681899c306badc63ac69b7d7</data>
