<node id="Israel">
  <data key="d0">Israel</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Israel is one of the primary locations where AMAT conducts its product development and manufacturing activities.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Israel is a location where the company has significant manufacturing operations and faces geopolitical challenges.&lt;SEP&gt;Israel is a region mentioned in the context of emergency conditions that could impact business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Israel is another foreign jurisdiction where the company earns a significant portion of its non-U.S. profits and is subject to tax rates that may change.&lt;SEP&gt;Israel is a geographic region that contributes to the company's revenues.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6295c9841b489759670dace2137e3d9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f20aa9a81d6ab585196c52c4b81c36f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a296116922ea376dbdc0f563507f5547&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db3fcbe26ec52d22abad5f9f0435fea6</data>
