<node id="Investing Activities">
  <data key="d0">Investing Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Investing Activities involves cash used for or generated from investments, such as capital expenditures and purchases or sales of investments.&lt;SEP&gt;Investing activities refer to the cash flows related to the acquisition and disposal of long-term assets and other investments for the fiscal year ended June 30, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Investing Activities refers to the cash flows from net proceeds from sale of securities and capital expenditures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b976a275590777e7877d2d66b5f6379c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfac3dde6482c2f8fd9ea0e0c659c15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcbd467e0d3d2d1e90e50929e4ef4372</data>
