<node id="Financing Activities">
  <data key="d0">Financing Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Financing Activities encompasses cash flows related to financing the company, including stock repurchases, dividends, and debt repayments.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing activities pertain to cash flows from financing the business, including debt repayments and stock repurchases, for the fiscal year ended June 30, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing Activities refers to the cash flows from repayment of debt, stock repurchases, and payment of dividends.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b976a275590777e7877d2d66b5f6379c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfac3dde6482c2f8fd9ea0e0c659c15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcbd467e0d3d2d1e90e50929e4ef4372</data>
