  <data key="d2">The effective tax rate for fiscal 2025 was higher than the prior fiscal year primarily due to a remeasurement of deferred tax assets resulting from new tax incentive agreements in Singapore.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The effective tax rate is the ratio of the actual taxes paid for a period to the pre-tax income for the same period.&lt;SEP&gt;The ratio of income tax expense to income before taxes.</data>
