  <data key="d2">The provision for income taxes and effective tax rates are affected by the geographical composition of pre-tax income, which includes jurisdictions with differing tax rates.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Provision for Income Taxes is the amount set aside for income tax payments, amounting to $302 in 2026 and $934 in 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Provision for Income Taxes is a component of the company's financial statements, details of which are provided for the years 2025, 2024, and 2023.&lt;SEP&gt;Estimate of income taxes based on current and deferred taxes.</data>
