<node id="Management">
  <data key="d0">Management</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Management is responsible for assessing and managing material risks from cybersecurity threats, including implementing risk mitigation plans and processes.&lt;SEP&gt;Management refers to the team or individuals responsible for overseeing the operations and strategic direction of a company, in this case, evaluating the company's performance using both GAAP and non-GAAP financial measures.&lt;SEP&gt;Management refers to the team of executives and leaders responsible for the daily operations and strategic direction of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d30ee8565f60986af2412d44782de3b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28d0d279e198946ca35e2e93f3701350&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d780eacfb91e291d22055bf3aca31fa3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
