<node id="Cybersecurity Risk Management Program">
  <data key="d0">Cybersecurity Risk Management Program</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The cybersecurity risk management program is a method employed by the company to assess, identify, and manage material risks from cybersecurity threats.&lt;SEP&gt;The Cybersecurity Risk Management Program is a program managed by the CISO, involving risk mitigation plans, processes, and controls.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d30ee8565f60986af2412d44782de3b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f533007cd8f65f3f88984fedd522d05d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
