  <data key="d0">Information Technology Security Teams</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Information technology security teams are involved in reviews that inform management's efforts to prevent, detect, mitigate, and remediate cybersecurity risks and incidents.</data>
