</node>
<node id="Intangible Assets">
  <data key="d0">Intangible Assets</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Intangible assets are non-physical assets such as patents and trademarks, which are reviewed for impairment and not amortized if they have indefinite useful lives.&lt;SEP&gt;Intangible assets are non-physical assets such as patents, trademarks, and goodwill that have value in helping a company earn future economic benefits.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-625ca1cf50e3b24380c8601c96bdd7a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25056dc4aba0a40a47c338bbf9630c33</data>
