  <data key="d2">The company is involved in various operations, including acquisitions, legal proceedings, and sustainability strategies.&lt;SEP&gt;The Company is an entity that has determined Pillar Two did not have a material impact on its financial statements or operations for the fiscal year ended March 31, 2025.|&lt;SEP&gt;The Company is involved in share-based compensation, goodwill assessment, and income tax accounting.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The Company is an organization that experiences financial events such as impairment charges and tax valuation allowances.</data>
