  <data key="d2">The U.S. Commerce Department Bureau of Industry and Security is a government agency responsible for enforcing export control regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The U.S. Commerce Department Bureau of Industry and Security is an organization that Applied Materials, Inc. had a legal settlement with to resolve export controls compliance matter.&lt;SEP&gt;The U.S. Commerce Department Bureau of Industry and Security is an organization that Applied Materials, Inc. had an agreed settlement with to resolve export controls compliance matters.</data>
