  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Integrated Circuits are complex electronic circuits fabricated on a single substrate, which are affected by export regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Integrated Circuits are electronic components used in various devices and are part of the semiconductor industry.</data>
