<node id="AI">
  <data key="d0">AI</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Artificial Intelligence (AI) is a rapidly evolving technology that significantly impacts the industries served by Applied Materials, driving demand for their products.&lt;SEP&gt;AI refers to Artificial Intelligence, a field driving demand for advanced processors and computing capabilities across various markets.&lt;SEP&gt;AI refers to artificial intelligence, a field where increasing complexity and value of semiconductor packages, particularly for AI and HPC applications, is driving significant growth in KLAC's advanced packaging business.&lt;SEP&gt;AI refers to Artificial Intelligence, a technology that the company and its competitors use, and which poses risks related to its use.&lt;SEP&gt;AI refers to artificial intelligence technologies that are increasingly used to perpetrate cyberattacks and could be integrated into KLA's, its customers', or business partners' operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Artificial Intelligence is a rapidly evolving technology that the company incorporates into its operations, products, and services, posing various competitive, legal, and regulatory risks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d8ee469fd420dd945b64b580faff532&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5068f4b1da4cd023617e872a463eeb62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4612ab0f41075ef25aa4070b5715ec41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e39760d10a53b7326a952678788b4f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e74b16856b8a1a3ddf8e77f75d7175ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-940cea73a3ab3826472368a5d0f388bc</data>
