<node id="Repurchase Program">
  <data key="d0">Repurchase Program</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Repurchase Program is an authorization for AMD to repurchase up to $12 billion of its common stock, funded by cash from operations, without a termination date and subject to suspension or discontinuation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Repurchase Program is an authorization for AMD to repurchase up to $12 billion of its common stock, funded by cash from operations, without a termination date and subject to suspension or discontinuation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Repurchase Program is an initiative by AMD to repurchase up to $14 billion of its common stock, funded by cash from operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Repurchase Program is an initiative by AMD to repurchase up to $14 billion of its common stock, funded by operational cash flow.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bde81dfa7c0130867695a7023e89cf63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0a83ce1ab52e2df80576ef179eeec72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42b87cf93df46f504c0e370bbcbc6d94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54b2dd7afb5853f7b9fcb8fff6544b20</data>
