  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that enacted a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that enacted a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that enacted a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that includes a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.</data>
