</node>
<node id="Arm GPUs">
  <data key="d0">Arm GPUs</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Arm GPUs are graphics processing units designed by Arm, which can be combined with Arm CPUs in chip designs.</data>
