</node>
<node id="Item 8. Financial Information-Note 1 - Description of Business and Summary of Significant Accounting Policies">
  <data key="d0">Item 8. Financial Information-Note 1 - Description of Business and Summary of Significant Accounting Policies</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Item 8. Financial Information-Note 1 - Description of Business and Summary of Significant Accounting Policies is a section in the Annual Report detailing the company's significant accounting policies and practices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f5952f8b9b70d6c7a8ac3693a20d7033</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777262484</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
