<node id="Royalty Revenue">
  <data key="d0">Royalty Revenue</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Royalty revenue is recognized based on the shipment of chips containing the company's products, using estimates and adjustments as actual sales data becomes available.&lt;SEP&gt;Royalty Revenue is a part of total revenue, influenced by chip shipments and royalty rates per chip.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1bd342ebc79b6c8d6a4c0db7019159b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca207bb382651453029b45cb72e9feff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a917696681899c306badc63ac69b7d7</data>
