  <data key="d0">Nasdaq</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Nasdaq is a stock exchange where the Company's ADSs are traded, and it is used as a reference for determining the fair value of share-based awards.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Nasdaq is the stock exchange where the Company’s ADSs are traded, and it is used to determine the fair value of RSUs.&gt;</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8e2d85f7a44ae4d46a5296c95183929c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1fc03c6340e9f91435287101b7ba57e5</data>
