  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Reporting Unit is an entity identified for the purpose of assessing goodwill impairment.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Reporting Unit is a component of a company for which discrete financial information is available and used in assessing goodwill for impairment.</data>
