  <data key="d0">Tape-Out</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Tape-out is the event when a customer's semiconductor chip design is sent for manufacturing, triggering a decision on which products to deploy in their chip.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ca207bb382651453029b45cb72e9feff</data>
