  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Software development tools are provided to companies developing chips based on the company's products, aiding engineers in writing and debugging software on Arm processors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ca207bb382651453029b45cb72e9feff</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
