<node id="Operating Cash Flows">
  <data key="d0">Operating Cash Flows</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Operating cash flows are a measure of the amount of cash generated or used by a company's operating activities.&lt;SEP&gt;Operating cash flows refer to the cash generated or used by a company's primary business operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-37906de44c22f23501372f2b90cd5aa7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25056dc4aba0a40a47c338bbf9630c33</data>
