<node id="PCB Business">
  <data key="d0">PCB Business</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The PCB business is a unit within the company that focuses on printed circuit board production.&lt;SEP&gt;PCB Business is a segment of the company that experienced a long-term forecast deterioration, leading to impairment tests and a pre-reorganization goodwill impairment charge.&lt;SEP&gt;The PCB Business is part of the company's reportable segment that experienced a deterioration in its long-term forecast.&lt;SEP&gt;The PCB Business is part of the company's operations, which experienced a deterioration in its long-term forecast.&lt;SEP&gt;The PCB Business is part of the company and is experiencing a long-term forecast deterioration, leading to impairment charges.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-37906de44c22f23501372f2b90cd5aa7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8c3943d4fcccf1ae19651cf71f87bf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b79e4b75a425925add250c81fbb9b71&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19032b9d0addd28842932a48ea8fd697&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d780eacfb91e291d22055bf3aca31fa3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
