<node id="California Credit Carry-Forwards">
  <data key="d0">California Credit Carry-Forwards</data>
  <data key="d1">financialasset</data>
  <data key="d2">California credit carry-forwards are tax credits that can be carried forward from one tax year to the next to offset future tax liabilities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-37906de44c22f23501372f2b90cd5aa7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777306896</data>
