</node>
<node id="Revenues">
  <data key="d0">Revenues</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Revenues refer to the total income generated from the main operations of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;The income derived from the sales of our products, which could be affected by various factors including product acceptance and pricing.&lt;SEP&gt;Revenues are the total income generated from the sales of goods or services related to the company's primary operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Revenues represent the income generated by the company, which is affected by various factors including customer base concentration, capital equipment procurement schedules, and foreign currency exchange rates.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-37906de44c22f23501372f2b90cd5aa7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4cef59817c38511355f56938f73f6db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25056dc4aba0a40a47c338bbf9630c33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-940cea73a3ab3826472368a5d0f388bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1329332311e82d0b2cc6f7232bfaa092</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
