<node id="Stock Repurchase Program">
  <data key="d0">Stock Repurchase Program</data>
  <data key="d1">financialprogram</data>
  <data key="d2">The Stock Repurchase Program is an initiative to repurchase company shares to mitigate dilution from equity incentive plans and return excess cash to stockholders.&lt;SEP&gt;The Stock Repurchase Program is a financial program with $5.03 billion remaining for repurchases as of June 30, 2025.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bfac3dde6482c2f8fd9ea0e0c659c15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d34b219513d1d4953f831b7693287834</data>
