<node id="KLAC">
  <data key="d0">KLAC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">KLAC is a leading supplier of process control and yield management solutions and services for the semiconductor and related electronics industries. It provides inspection and metrology products, services, software, and other offerings that support R&amp;D and manufacturing of ICs, wafers, and reticles.&lt;SEP&gt;KLAC is a company with securities that are subject to various risks affecting its business, financial condition, and operations.&lt;SEP&gt;KLAC is a company that issues financial reports and is subject to various regulations and market conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4612ab0f41075ef25aa4070b5715ec41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e39760d10a53b7326a952678788b4f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6430e92774e5a3f258ef2544910d4dd5</data>
