<node id="U.S. Entity List">
  <data key="d0">U.S. Entity List</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">The U.S. Entity List is a reference document that includes certain entities with which the use of U.S. technology to manufacture products is restricted, requiring export licenses for related semiconductor capital equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;The U.S. Entity List is a list of parties that are generally ineligible to receive U.S.-regulated items without prior licensing from the Commerce Department, mentioned in the context of export controls影响到KLAC's operations in China.&lt;SEP&gt;The U.S. Entity List is a list maintained by the U.S. government that includes parties generally ineligible to receive U.S.-regulated items without prior licensing.&lt;SEP&gt;The U.S. Entity List is a list by the U.S. government that includes companies like Huawei and others with restrictions on trade.&lt;SEP&gt;The U.S. Entity List is a list of parties that are generally ineligible to receive U.S.-regulated items without prior licensing from BIS.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4612ab0f41075ef25aa4070b5715ec41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0f7533f1c0231555ac5ae30f4d37842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-120a4f2fbe48d0891e48fba271c88ec1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69ff95667fb52350500821b847289ef6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db3fcbe26ec52d22abad5f9f0435fea6</data>
