  <data key="d0">Specialty Semiconductor Process</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Specialty Semiconductor Process is a segment that includes etching and deposition solutions for advanced packaging and specialty semiconductor markets, with increased revenue primarily due to the advanced packaging business.&lt;SEP&gt;The Specialty Semiconductor Process is a reportable segment of the company that was affected by the internal reorganization.&lt;SEP&gt;Specialty Semiconductor Process refers to advanced vacuum deposition and etching process tools used by a broad range of specialty semiconductor customers.&lt;SEP&gt;The Specialty Semiconductor Process is a reportable segment within a company that is affected by reorganization and undergoes goodwill impairment tests.&lt;SEP&gt;Specialty Semiconductor Process is a revenue segment that experienced growth in revenues during the specified periods.&lt;SEP&gt;Specialty Semiconductor Process is a segment that includes etching and deposition solutions for advanced packaging and specialty semiconductor markets.</data>
