<node id="KLA">
  <data key="d0">KLA</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">KLA is the company reporting its financial performance, including revenues, costs, and net income, and focusing on returning cash to investors through share repurchases and dividends.&lt;SEP&gt;KLA is an organization that owns and maintains IT Systems and faces cybersecurity risks, including threats to the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of its IT Systems and Confidential Information.&lt;SEP&gt;KLA is a company that earns significant profits in Singapore and is affected by tax incentives and potential top-up tax.&lt;SEP&gt;KLA is a leading supplier of process control and yield management solutions and services for the semiconductor and related electronics industries.&lt;SEP&gt;KLA is a company affected by the BIS Rules, restricted from providing certain U.S. origin tools, software, and technology to certain wafer fab equipment manufacturers located in China without an export license.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c0f7533f1c0231555ac5ae30f4d37842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e74b16856b8a1a3ddf8e77f75d7175ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a296116922ea376dbdc0f563507f5547&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3082390d4ae9b34c69f94e2ec0135c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db3fcbe26ec52d22abad5f9f0435fea6</data>
