  <data key="d1">contract</data>
  <data key="d2">The Credit Agreement is a new financial agreement replacing the Prior Revolving Credit Facility, with a maturity date of July 3, 2030, and options for extension.&lt;SEP&gt;The Credit Agreement is a new financial agreement that replaced the Prior Revolving Credit Facility, with a maturity date of July 3, 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;The Credit Agreement is the agreement governing the Revolving Credit Facility and includes terms and covenants.</data>
