  <data key="d1">regulation</data>
  <data key="d2">The 2023 BIS Rules updated the export controls on advanced computing semiconductors and manufacturing equipment, affecting trade with certain countries including China.&lt;SEP&gt;The 2023 BIS Rules updated export controls on advanced computing semiconductors and semiconductor manufacturing equipment, as well as items that support supercomputing applications and end-uses, to arms embargoed countries, including China.</data>
