  <data key="d1">regulation</data>
  <data key="d2">The 2024 BIS Rules added more companies to the U.S. Entity List and revised the definition of advanced DRAM, further restricting trade with China.&lt;SEP&gt;The 2024 BIS Rules added more companies to the U.S. Entity List and revised the definition of advanced DRAM, further restricting the ability to provide certain items and services to facilities in China producing advanced DRAM ICs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-69ff95667fb52350500821b847289ef6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db3fcbe26ec52d22abad5f9f0435fea6</data>
