  <data key="d0">Microsoft Azure</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Microsoft Azure is an industry leader supporting the expansion of the Arm compute platform, with Azure Cobalt family of CPUs built on Neoverse CSS.&lt;SEP&gt;Microsoft Azure is a platform that has developed the Azure Cobalt family of CPUs, built on Neoverse CSS, as stated by Rani Borkar.</data>
