<node id="Arm AGI CPU">
  <data key="d0">Arm AGI CPU</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Arm AGI CPU is the first Arm-designed data center CPU for agentic AI infrastructure, offering more than 2x performance per rack compared to x86 platforms. It is expected to be the foundation for agentic data centers and is backed by a strong global ecosystem.&lt;SEP&gt;The Arm AGI CPU is a product that marks the next phase of Arm's evolution into data center silicon, designed for AI infrastructure at scale.&lt;SEP&gt;The Arm AGI CPU is a purpose-built AI compute platform that creates new opportunities for deeper collaboration across silicon design, memory integration, and manufacturing innovation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e303b18ab63b26668de99eef62a26b7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fc487cdc1541b708566fbf837bf0441&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d1f6742e80ed84d267cfe46fa7c9e31</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777308127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
