  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Rene Haas is the CEO of Arm Holdings plc, who stated that the expansion into delivering production silicon with the Arm AGI CPU marks the next phase of the Arm compute platform and a defining moment for the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d1f6742e80ed84d267cfe46fa7c9e31</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777308127</data>
